Package: ggauto
Title: Automatically create and style 'ggplot2' charts
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Nicola", "Rennie", , "nrennie.research@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: `ggauto` is an *opinionated* `ggplot2` extension package to
    automatically choose the best chart type and styling, based on the
    types and values in the data.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Depends: 
    R (>= 4.1)
